<HL>
   Economy:
   Court Strikes Down Fed Policy Forcing
   Bank Holding Firms to Help Sick Units
   ----
   By Paul Duke Jr. and Michael Allen
   Staff Reporters of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/16/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
</SO>
<CO>
